So you have no idea.

01:27:58.145 --> 01:28:00.198
LAURA: It's less than a mile down, I know.

01:28:00.198 --> 01:28:03.906
MARISHA: It kind of rushes past you really fast,
it's a little disorienting.

01:28:03.906 --> 01:28:06.245
LAURA: Okay.

01:28:06.245 --> 01:28:08.352
LIAM: No traps?

01:28:08.352 --> 01:28:10.332
MATT: No traps at the moment, no.

01:28:10.332 --> 01:28:12.192
LAURA: Should we all stealth?

01:28:12.192 --> 01:28:16.047
PATRICK: These are just here so that people step
