01:28:33.703 --> 01:28:35.396
TRAVIS: Plus ten?

01:28:35.396 --> 01:28:36.486
LAURA: 30.

01:28:36.486 --> 01:28:37.714
LIAM: 35.

01:28:37.714 --> 01:28:41.843
TALIESIN: 34. And then Scanlan...

01:28:41.843 --> 01:28:43.347
MARISHA: 30 total.

01:28:43.347 --> 01:28:44.505
TRAVIS: 28.

01:28:44.505 --> 01:28:45.682
LAURA: 25 for Pike.

01:28:45.682 --> 01:28:49.901
TRAVIS: No, sorry. Oh, 30.

01:28:49.901 --> 01:28:51.919
TALIESIN: 18 for Scanlan.

01:28:51.919 --> 01:28:54.278
PATRICK: 29 for me.

01:28:54.278 --> 01:29:01.079
MATT: Great, awesome. All right, so, as you guys
continue progressing down this curving tunnel, it

01:29:01.079 --> 01:29:05.266
goes into a very, very mild descent.

01:29:05.266 --> 01:29:15.430
MARISHA: Can I do-- I wanna do a quick check. This
is some Bones-type shit. Can I see if these bones

01:29:15.430 --> 01:29:21.204
were charred recently, or once again, if these
